ZH: 他利用他的努力功成名就。
EN: He achieved fame through his hard work.

ZH: 这是我多年来奋斗的努力功。
EN: This is the result of years of effort on my part.

ZH: 我们应该认可他的功，而不是批评他的失败。
EN: We should recognize his achievements, not criticize his failures.

ZH: 她的功在公司中是不可或缺的。
EN: Her contribution to the company is indispensable.

ZH: 要取得成功，需要付出很多的努力功。
EN: To succeed, one needs to put in a lot of effort.

ZH: 她的功一直得到了上司的肯定。
EN: Her achievements have always been acknowledged by her superiors.

ZH: 必须承认，他的功在这个项目中很明显。
EN: It must be acknowledged that his contribution to this project is significant.

ZH: 只有通过不懈的工作，才能创造更大的功。
EN: Only through relentless work can greater achievements be made.

ZH: 她的功被公认是这个领域的佼佼者。
EN: Her accomplishments are widely recognized in this field.

ZH: 必须给予那些为公司做出卓越贡献的人以表彰他们的功。
EN: Recognition must be given to those who make outstanding contributions to the company.

ZH: 他是一个肯定我们努力功的人。
EN: He is someone who appreciates our efforts.

ZH: 在这个团队中，每个人的努力功都非常重要。
EN: In this team, everyone's contributions are very important.

ZH: 只有不懈的努力功才能带来成功。
EN: Only unrelenting effort can bring success.

ZH: 他的努力功带来了丰硕的成果。
EN: His hard work has brought fruitful results.

ZH: 这个项目的成功离不开每个人的努力功。
EN: The success of this project is inseparable from everyone's efforts.

ZH: 让我们一起努力功，让公司更加繁荣昌盛。
EN: Let's work together to make the company more prosperous.

ZH: 他的功使得这个社区更加美好。
EN: His efforts have made this community a better place.

ZH: 她勤劳的功使她成为了一个典范。
EN: Her hard work has made her a role model.

ZH: 这些功不是一夜之间造就的，而是长期的积累。
EN: These accomplishments were not achieved overnight, but through long-term accumulation.

ZH: 只有通过努力功才能享受到成功的果实。
EN: Only through hard work can one enjoy the fruits of success.
